        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/d/ccd318/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-06-30T09:42:43.182Z",
        "cooked": "<p>So, firstly, yes, doing a fresh install on a new phone with a different phone number would not only result in an account with no chat history, all contacts would also not be there, because the account would be a completely different one.</p>\n<p>I don’t know why this request suddenly appeared, it may have been due to some update (of Signal or the OS) or some other issue. It’s hard to say in retrospect.</p>\n<p>Generally, a landline number is supported as long as it can receive SMS.</p>\n<p>According to this</p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/de/articles/360008216551-Signal-installieren#ipad_separate\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      \n\n      <a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/de/articles/360008216551-Signal-installieren#ipad_separate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Signal-Support</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://support.signal.org/hc/de/articles/360008216551-Signal-installieren#ipad_separate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Signal installieren</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Schnell, einfach, sicher. Signal ist Privatsphäre, die in deine Tasche (oder auf deinen Schreibtisch) passt.\nLade Signal&nbsp;hier herunter oder befolge die Installationsschritte für deine Plattform.\n\nA...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>There should be a very tiny symbol in the upper right corner to click, that should allow setting it up as it was. Then, you should follow the suggested steps, making sure to use your Signal PIN, if you have one, in case you are asked.</p>\n<p>Depending on the reason that caused the issues there is still no guarantee that this will restore the data, but it is your best option.</p>\n<p>You can’t get a backup from the app if you hadn’t made one before. If you are responsible for this person’s Signal account, it might be worth setting up a backup, as soon as this functionality is available for iOS/iPadOS, but that can’t help you right now.</p>\n<p>Kindly<br>\ndesert nip</p>",
